dmca.title: DMCA notice to www.money-to-rates.com
dmca.body:
Our site money-rates.com was registered in 1999 and has been recognized as a leading financial services site for 8 years. In May of 2007 the domain money-to-rates.com was registered and all of our original content, code, graphics, and design was copied on to this brand new site including all interior pages with our detailed bank rate reports. money-to-rates.con is attempting to confuse advertisers and divert advertising revenue by contacting the banks regarding the cloned site. This has been identified by authorities as an act of bank fraud as well as copyright infringement. This letter serves as notice to cease-and-desist these activities immediately.

money-rates.com: registered 1999, recognized in Wall Street Journal, USA Today and other publications as financial source

money-to-rates.com: registered 2007, cloned our site May 2007
